## 🎭 Role Adopted: 🧪 QA Engineer

### Expectations
- Provide a short, high-signal manual test plan for affected areas.
- Prefer regression coverage for storefront + dashboard + Apps Script changes.

### Must-cover areas
- Storefront: product load, filters, modal options, cart totals, WhatsApp checkout
- Compare: add/remove, toast, comparison table renders
- Dashboard: login gate, data fetch, status update, stock sync, polling behavior
